## New Box CLI launched

We've launched a new version of the Box CLI, so you can: 
* Authenticate instantly with your own Box credentials via OAuth
* Automate complex, multi-step workflows — upload files, extract metadata, apply watermarks, trigger document signing — all from the command line
* Give your AI agents a composable interface to retrieve, transform, and act on content in Box without extra configuration

Developers and agents can now work together seamlessly, with Box content at the center. To learn more, visit our [cli][BoxCLIdocumentation].

The Box CLI works with agentic tools and harnesses, letting you manage content, automate tasks, and integrate Box into scripts, tools, and AI agents.

